Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.97,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧 祗王泠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.97,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,消えろ 祇王泠呀ぁぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.46,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.46,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.38,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 愁生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.38,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,どうした 愁生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.80,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,又增加了一股强大的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.80,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,大きな力が　またひとつ増えた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.46,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.46,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,それって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:01.10,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 没错 是路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:01.10,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 間違いない　ルカだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.09,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.09,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,ルカ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.54,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 夕月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.54,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫か　夕月
