Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:49.22,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:47.97,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:47.97,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,単純な所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:49.26,cn.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 喂我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:49.26,jp.sub,NTP,0,0,0,,そうさ　あのな